sCellEventTrap_07_09.name: sCellEventTrap_07_09

sCellEventTrap_0b_0b.name: sCellEventTrap_0b_0b
sCellEventTrap_0b_0b.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The preserving resync process has been initiated and is progressing.

sCellEventTrap_0b_0c.name: sCellEventTrap_0b_0c
sCellEventTrap_0b_0c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A periodic system monitoring event has been generated to report current status.

sCellEventTrap_0b_0d.name: sCellEventTrap_0b_0d
sCellEventTrap_0b_0d.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The other controller has been shut down because of a previous failed codeload. A new codeload must be completed before restarting the other controller. Then the other controller can be manually restarted.

sCellEventTrap_0c_03.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_03
sCellEventTrap_0c_03.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. The specified Data Replication Group has transitioned to the Merging state, because the Data Replication Destination Storage System is now accessible or resumed.

sCellEventTrap_0c_04.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_04
sCellEventTrap_0c_04.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Data Replication Group has entered the Failsafe Locked state because the Data Replication Destination Storage System is inaccessible.

sCellEventTrap_0c_05.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_05
sCellEventTrap_0c_05.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Data Replication Group has entered the Failsafe Locked state due to an inaccessible Destination Virtual Disk.

sCellEventTrap_0c_06.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_06
sCellEventTrap_0c_06.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Full Copy was terminated prior to completion: An unrecoverable read error occurred on the specified Source Virtual Disk during the Full Copy.

sCellEventTrap_0c_07.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_07
sCellEventTrap_0c_07.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Full Copy terminated prior to completion: A remote copy error occurred due to an inaccessible alternate Storage System; The Full Copy will continue when the Data Replication Destination is restored.

sCellEventTrap_0c_08.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_08
sCellEventTrap_0c_08.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. A Full Copy terminated prior to completion: A remote copy error occurred due to an inaccessible Destination Virtual Disk; The Full Copy will continue when the Destination Virtual Disk is restored.

sCellEventTrap_0c_09.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_09
sCellEventTrap_0c_09.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. Data Replication Log for the specified Data Replication Group has reached its maximum capacity; The Data Replication Group has been marked for a Full Copy; Evaluate the need to manually resize the Data Replication Log for affected Data Replication Group.

sCellEventTrap_0c_0a.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_0a
sCellEventTrap_0c_0a.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Data Replication Log has been reset due to a Data Replication Group failover.

sCellEventTrap_0c_0b.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_0b
sCellEventTrap_0c_0b.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. An unrecoverable read error occurred on the specified Data Replication Group Data Replication Log logical disk during a background read.

sCellEventTrap_0c_0c.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_0c
sCellEventTrap_0c_0c.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Destination Data Replication Group has successfully completed a Merge.

sCellEventTrap_0c_0f.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_0f
sCellEventTrap_0c_0f.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Data Replication Group is no longer in a Failsafe Locked state.

sCellEventTrap_0c_10.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_10
sCellEventTrap_0c_10.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A Destination Data Replication Group has been marked for a Full Copy.

sCellEventTrap_0c_11.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_11
sCellEventTrap_0c_11.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. This Data Replication Group is transitioning from a Data Replication Source role to a Data Replication Destination role.

sCellEventTrap_0c_12.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_12
sCellEventTrap_0c_12.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. This Data Replication Group is transitioning from a Data Replication Destination role to a Data Replication Source role.

sCellEventTrap_0c_15.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_15
sCellEventTrap_0c_15.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The Data Replication Path between this Storage System and the Peer Storage System has closed, possibly due to a connection failure between the specified host port and the Peer Storage System.

sCellEventTrap_0c_16.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_16
sCellEventTrap_0c_16.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. A controller has sent a time report message to this controller.

sCellEventTrap_0c_17.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_17
sCellEventTrap_0c_17.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The Data Replication Manager communications protocol version between the Data Replication Source Storage System and a Data Replication Destination Storage System is mismatched.

sCellEventTrap_0c_18.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_18
sCellEventTrap_0c_18.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. Conditions on the Data Replication Destination Storage System are preventing acceptable replication throughput: Initiating temporary logging on the affected Data Replication Group that is failsafe mode disabled.

sCellEventTrap_0c_19.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_19
sCellEventTrap_0c_19.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. Overlapping concurrent host writes to an Active/Active Peer Storage System violate a Data Replication Manager architectural requirement, resulting in a reparative resynchronization operation for the master Storage System and a Full Copy operation.

sCellEventTrap_0c_1a.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_1a

sCellEventTrap_0c_1c.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_1c
sCellEventTrap_0c_1c.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. The specified Source Data Replication Group has transitioned to the (not merging) Logging state because a Destination Virtual Disk is not accessible.

sCellEventTrap_0c_1d.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_1d
sCellEventTrap_0c_1d.description: Severity: Normal -- informational in nature. Inconsistency was found in the group log: A Full Copy of the affected Data Replication Group will be initiated.

sCellEventTrap_0c_1e.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_1e
sCellEventTrap_0c_1e.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. sCellEventTrap_0c_1f.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_1f

sCellEventTrap_0c_20.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_20
sCellEventTrap_0c_20.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. sCellEventTrap_0c_21.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_21
sCellEventTrap_0c_21.description: Severity: Critical -- failure or failure imminent. sCellEventTrap_0c_22.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_22

sCellEventTrap_0c_23.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_23
sCellEventTrap_0c_23.description: Severity: Warning -- not failed but attention recommended or required. Conditions on the inter site link are preventing acceptable replication throughput: Initiating temporary logging on the affected Data Replication Group that is failsafe mode disabled.

sCellEventTrap_0c_24.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_24

sCellEventTrap_0c_25.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_25

sCellEventTrap_0c_26.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_26

sCellEventTrap_0c_27.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_27

sCellEventTrap_0c_28.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_28

sCellEventTrap_0c_2a.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_2a

sCellEventTrap_0c_33.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_33

sCellEventTrap_0c_36.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_36

sCellEventTrap_0c_37.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_37

sCellEventTrap_0c_39.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_39

sCellEventTrap_0c_3e.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_3e

sCellEventTrap_0c_3f.name: sCellEventTrap_0c_3f
